ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD (a) to adjust its accounts, as of December 31, 2004, by transferring to a separate account the undistributed funds in the 1996-1997 pool account for wheat and in the 1997-1998 accounts for wheat, amber durum wheat and designated barley; and (b) to pay to producers, out of that account, the amount to which they are entitled.
